subject re earthquak predict in articl mai atho rutger edu dan ingr com a rose aros write were god to call me to be a prophet and i were to misrepres god s word my call would be lost forev god s word would command the peopl never to listen to or fear my word as i would be a fals prophet my bridg would be burnt forev perhap i could repent and be save but i could never again be a prophet of god though there is a command in the law not to heed to on who propheci fals it is still possibl for the on who ha propheci fals to propheci trueli again take for exampl the stori in king about the man of god from judah who came to israel and propheci against a king the lord had command him to not eat or drink till he return home anoth prophet want thi man of god to stai in hi hous so he propheci fals that the lord want the man of god to stai in hi hous while thei at and drank in hi hous the lord gave the prophet who li a word that the man of god would die from break the word of the lord it came to pass link hudson 